Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.33,Pony,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.47,Pony,,0,0,0,,来吧 小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.35,Pony,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.76,Pony,,0,0,0,,交给你了 伙计
